articles.title: Julian McMahon’s Former ‘Fantastic Four,’ ‘Charmed’ and ‘Nip/Tuck’ Co-Stars Share Tributes - The Hollywood Reporter
articles.description: The Australian actor died Wednesday in Clearwater, Florida.
articles.content:
Julian McMahon‘s former co-stars and more of Hollywood are mourning his loss. 
The Australian actor died on Wednesday in Clearwater, Florida, following a battle with cancer, The Hollywood confirmed.… [+3574 chars]
